<h1>Contribute</h1>


<p>
  We would be happy if you want to contribute to this pattern language, may it be you want to correct a typo, add known uses, make pattern suggestions or anything else. In that case you have the following options:
<p>
<ul>
  <li>Open or comment on any of the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/restalk/restalk-patterns/issues">issues</a> on GitHub.</li>
  <li>Fork the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/restalk/restalk-patterns">repository</a> and create a <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/using-pull-requests/">pull request</a>.</li>
  <li>Write an e-mail to <a href="mailto:mail@restalk-patterns.org">mail@restalk-patterns.org</a>.</li>
  <li>Follow us on Twitter: <a target="_blank"  href="https://twitter.com/RESTalkPatterns">@RESTalkPatterns</a>.</li>
  <li>Create your own patterns or conversation models by using this <a href="img/notation_horizontal.svg" download>SVG file</a> as starting point.</li>
</ul>
